The deep UI upgrade for all `jin-hong-me-html-v2` interior pages is officially complete. We synthesized premium ThemeForest (MaxCoach) patterns coupled with specific UI concepts from your legacy portfolio to reconstruct a modern, unified, enterprise-grade architecture.

