### Key Achievements:
- **Consistent UX Master Layout**: Applied the unified, professional Header and Footer (dark variant) to all pages.
- **Hero Breadcrumb Protocol**: All interior pages now feature the standardized hero section (`.breadcrumb-area`) using `hero-bg.jpg` layered with a semi-transparent blue/black gradient.
- **Zero-Emoji Enforcement**: Stripped all illegal raw emojis from HTML source codes (e.g., [honors.html](file:///C:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/jin-hong-me-html/honors.html)) and replaced them exclusively with highly scalable, consistent FontAwesome v6 solid icons.
- **Conversion Optimization**: Integrated the universal Floating WhatsApp CTA (`.float-wa`) onto the bottom right of all active V2 pages, identical to legacy project behaviors.
- **Premium Interactivity**: Introduced elegant CSS transitions across cards (e.g., `.service-card`, `.project-card`), transforming on hover (shadow diffusion, vertical translation).

